-- Assurant Cuts Florida Insurance Rates 10% in Deal With Regulator
-- B y   Z a c h a r y   T r a c e r
-- 2013-10-08T15:49:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-08/assurant-cuts-florida-insurance-rates-10-in-deal-with-regulator.html
Assurant Inc. (AIZ) , under pressure from
Florida regulators, agreed to cut rates 10 percent in the state
for home insurance that borrowers must buy when they miss
payments on their initial policies.  The new rates are expected to be effective in the first
quarter of next year, the New York-based insurer said today in a
statement distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
